---
// Hero.astro
---

<div class="flex flex-col items-center justify-center text-center px-6 pt-12 pb-4">
  <h1 class="text-3xl sm:text-4xl md:text-5xl font-extrabold text-white tracking-tight font-(family-name:--font-display) leading-[1.1] mb-5">
    Aprende Processing<br>
    <span class="text-blue-400">desde cero.</span>
  </h1>

  <p class="text-base md:text-lg text-white/45 leading-relaxed mb-4">
    Curso para Industrias gráficas, con ejercicios prácticos paso a paso.
  </p>
</div>

<div class="flex flex-wrap justify-center gap-3">
  <span class="inline-flex items-center gap-1.5 text-xs text-white/30 bg-white/[0.03] border border-white/[0.06] rounded-full px-3 py-1.5">
    <svg class="w-3.5 h-3.5 text-blue-400/60" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" aria-hidden="true">
      <polygon points="13 2 3 14 12 14 11 22 21 10 12 10 13 2"></polygon>
    </svg>
    +55 clases
  </span>

  <span class="inline-flex items-center gap-1.5 text-xs text-white/30 bg-white/[0.03] border border-white/[0.06] rounded-full px-3 py-1.5">
    <svg class="w-3.5 h-3.5 text-blue-400/60" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" aria-hidden="true">
      <polyline points="16 18 22 12 16 6"></polyline>
      <polyline points="8 6 2 12 8 18"></polyline>
    </svg>
    Ejercicios prácticos
  </span>

  <span class="inline-flex items-center gap-1.5 text-xs text-white/30 bg-white/[0.03] border border-white/[0.06] rounded-full px-3 py-1.5">
    <svg class="w-3.5 h-3.5 text-blue-400/60" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" aria-hidden="true">
      <path d="M12 22s8-4 8-10V5l-8-3-8 3v7c0 6 8 10 8 10z"></path>
    </svg>
    100% Gratuito
  </span>
</div>

